# Custom IDE shortcuts
Clone Caret Above: M-S-Up
Clone Caret Below: M-S-Down
Move Caret To Block Start/End: Remove C-]/C-[
Delete Line: Remove
Select Single Line at Caret: Possibly C-L
Manage Projects: C-K C-E
Undo: Remove C-Z
Redo: Remove C-Y
Find Next: Remove C-L
Find Previous: Remove M-C-L
Toggle Full Screen Mode: M-F11
Toggle Zen Mode: M-C-F11
Cyclic Expand Word: M-/
Move Line Up: Remove
Move Line Down: Remove
Commit: C-K C-K
Pin Active Tool Window Tab: C-K C-P
Move Caret to Page Top: Remove (C-PgUp)
Move Caret to Page Bottom: Remove (C-PgDn)
